## UserFavorites [/api/users/:user_id/favorites/:project_id]

### POST

案件をお気に入りする <br>
Cacoo: 18, 21, 30, 31

+ Request (application/json)

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Attribute

        + code: 200 (number)
        + message: Success user_favorite create (string)

+ Response 400 (application/json)

    + Attribute

        + code: 400 (number)
        + message: Bad Request (string)

### DELETE

