Cacoo: 18, 21, 30, 31

+ Request (application/json)

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Attribute

        + code: 200 (number)
        + message: Success user_favorite delete (string)

+ Response 400 (application/json)

    + Attribute

        + code: 400 (number)
        + message: Bad Request (string)
